    "We define a case as invalid if the validation fails and set the corresponding explicit and implicit probabilities as np.nan so that it is not used in the evaluation.",
    "Accuracy, AUROC, and AUPRC are used as the evaluation metrics.",
    "All experiments are run three times with different LLM temperatures (0, 0.3, and 0.7), and the average and standard deviation of these metrics are calculated and reported across the three runs.",
    "AUROC is the primary metric as it is the most common metric for the probability prediction.",
    "AUPRC is used to compare the performance difference on imbalanced data experiments."
